OL,3,C'Will it ever be put right?': Ex-
OL,4,Csubpostmasters on Post Office inquiry
OL,5,Cfindings
OL,7,FSubpostmasters whose lives were ruined
OL,8,Fby the Post Office spoke to ITV News
OL,9,FReporter Ellie Pitt about what the
OL,10,Ffindings of the inquiry mean to them
OL,11,Fand how their fight for justice is far
OL,12,Ffrom over
OL,14,FFormer subpostmasters affected by the
OL,15,FHorizon IT scandal have welcomed the
OL,16,Fdamning first report from the official
OL,17,Finquiry, saying it shows the "full
OL,18,Fscale of the horror that they
OL,19,Funleashed on us".
