OL,3,C'Will it ever be put right?': Ex-
OL,4,Csubpostmasters on Post Office inquiry
OL,5,Cfindings
OL,7,FIt's been called one of the worst
OL,8,Fmiscarriages of justice in British
OL,9,Flegal history, now a report into the
OL,10,FHorizon IT scandal has found Post
OL,11,FOffice bosses were aware the system
OL,12,Fwas faulty but "maintained a fiction"
OL,13,Fthat it was always accurate, having
OL,14,F"disastrous impacts".
OL,16,FApproximately 1,000 subpostmasters
OL,17,Fwere wrongfully convicted by the Post
OL,18,FOffice between 1999 and 2015, after
OL,19,Fthe Horizon IT software made it appear
OL,20,Fas if money was missing from their
OL,21,Faccounts.
