OL,3,C'Will it ever be put right?': Ex-
OL,4,Csubpostmasters on Post Office inquiry
OL,5,Cfindings
OL,7,FThe 162-page report by Sir Wyn
OL,8,FWilliams, published Tuesday, also
OL,9,Fconcluded that at least 13 people may
OL,10,Fhave taken their own lives after being
OL,11,Faccused of wrongdoing by the Post
OL,12,FOffice, and a further 59 people had
OL,13,Fcontemplated suicide as a result of
OL,14,Fstress from the scandal.
OL,16,FITV News has spoken to some of the
OL,17,Fsubpostmasters affected by the Horizon
OL,18,FIT scandal to hear their reaction to
OL,19,FSir Wyn Williams' report.
OL,21,FJo Hamilton
