OL,7,FTracy McFadden
OL,9,FTracy McFadden ran a post office in
OL,10,FDerbyshire for 14 years.
OL,12,FWhen Horizon was installed, her plan
OL,13,Fto retire came to a disastrous halt.
OL,15,FTracy's story was also retold in the
OL,16,FITV drama.
OL,18,FOne moment which played out on screen
OL,19,Fwas when Tracy rang the Horizon
OL,20,Fhelpline for guidance over a
OL,21,Fdiscrepancy of #1,000.
