OL,7,FShe then saw the sum double to #2,000,
OL,8,Fthen #4,000 and finally #16,000.
OL,10,FTracy had to turn to her family to
OL,11,Fborrow money, as well as take out
OL,12,Floans and credit cards to cover the
OL,13,Falleged missing money.
OL,15,FEventually, she had debt collectors
OL,16,Fturn up at her front door.
OL,18,FShe said: "I've been stabbed in the
OL,19,Fback terribly and it's about time that
OL,20,Fknife came out".
