OL,7,FSeema Misra was running a Post Office
OL,8,Fin Surrey in 2005 but was suspended in
OL,9,F2008 after being accused of stealing
OL,10,F#74,000.
OL,12,FShe was eight weeks pregnant with her
OL,13,Fsecond child when she was sentenced to
OL,14,F15 months imprisonment in 2010.
OL,16,FShe had her conviction quashed by the
OL,17,FCourt of Appeal in 2021.
OL,19,FShane Johnson
