OL,3,C'Will it ever be put right?': Ex-
OL,4,Csubpostmasters on Post Office inquiry
OL,5,Cfindings
OL,7,FShane Johnson took over the Post
OL,8,FOffice branch in Kirkby-in-Ashfield in
OL,9,F2003.
OL,11,FFor four years he had no trouble until
OL,12,Fthe organisation insisted he take over
OL,13,Fthe contract for a new cashpoint which
OL,14,Fwas linked to the Horizon IT system.
OL,16,FHe said: "Within weeks we suffered a
OL,17,Fcatastrophic loss. Things had been
OL,18,Flinked to the main computer which had
OL,19,Fnever been linked to our computers
OL,20,Fbefore.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
