OL,7,FHe eventually sold the business at a
OL,8,Floss and estimates, by adding up loss
OL,9,Fof future earnings, he is #665,000 out
OL,10,Fof pocket.
OL,12,FShane has now reached a settlement
OL,13,Fwith the Post Office.
OL,15,F"Will it ever be put right? I
OL,16,Fpersonally don't think so. Will there
OL,17,Fever be any accountability? I don't
OL,18,Fthink so," he said.
