OL,3,C'Will it ever be put right?': Ex-
OL,4,Csubpostmasters on Post Office inquiry
OL,5,Cfindings
OL,7,FBusiness Secretary Jonathan Reynolds
OL,8,Fsaid: "The publication of the Post
OL,9,FOffice Horizon IT Inquiry's report
OL,10,Ftoday by Sir Wyn and his team marks an
OL,11,Fimportant milestone for sub-
OL,12,Fpostmasters and their families.
OL,14,F"I welcome the publication today and
OL,15,Fam committed to ensuring wronged sub-
OL,16,Fpostmasters are given full, fair, and
OL,17,Fprompt redress.
