OL,4,Csubpostmasters on Post Office inquiry
OL,5,Cfindings
OL,7,F"The recommendations contained in Sir
OL,8,FWyn's report require careful
OL,9,Freflection, including on further
OL,10,Faction to complete the redress
OL,11,Fschemes. Government will promptly
OL,12,Frespond to the recommendations in full
OL,13,Fin Parliament."
OL,15,FPost Office Minister Gareth Thomas
OL,16,Fsaid: "I welcome the Inquiry's
OL,17,Fpublication today and pay tribute to
OL,18,FSir Wyn and his team for their
OL,19,Fcomprehensive and penetrating work.
