OL,3,C'Will it ever be put right?': Ex-
OL,4,Csubpostmasters on Post Office inquiry
OL,5,Cfindings
OL,7,F"We must never lose sight of the
OL,8,FHorizon Scandal's human impact on
OL,9,Fpostmasters and their families, which
OL,10,Fthe Inquiry has highlighted so well.
OL,12,F"Sir Wyn's report highlights a series
OL,13,Fof failings by the Post Office and
OL,14,Fvarious governments. His
OL,15,Frecommendations are immensely helpful
OL,16,Fas a guide for what is needed to
OL,17,Ffinish the job, and we will respond in
OL,18,Ffull to Parliament after carefully
OL,19,Fconsidering them."
